RawLine: ITEM_700059_Tip,將令牌給守衛看，可前往第四域。令牌正面有朱雀紋樣，並附有『崖下火噬，雲梯寸斷，長蔓代行，洞府一窺。』這段文字。,将令牌给守卫看，可前往第四域。令牌正面有朱雀纹样，并附有『崖下火噬，云梯寸断，长蔓代行，洞府一窥。』这段文字。

Items.mt: Show the token to the guard and you can go to the fourth domain. On the front of the token, there is a vermilion bird pattern, and it also has the text "The fire under the cliff is devouring, the cloud ladder is broken, the long vine is walking on behalf of the guard, and the cave is a glimpse. This text.
